{"word":"H7353 - רָחֵל - râchêl - raw-kale' - Ewe","slug":"H7353","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָחֵל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râchêl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-kale'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Ewe"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05D7;&#x05DC; - ra&#x0302;che&#x0302;l</b> - <i>raw-khale'</i><p/>From an unused root meaning to <i>journey</i>; a <i>ewe</i> (the <i>females</i> being the predominant element of a flock), (as a good <i>traveller</i>): - ewe, sheep."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7354\">H7354</a>"}]}